sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Production
    participant H as Health Checks
    participant M as Cloud Monitoring
    participant R as Rollout Controller
    P->>H: Validate deployment
    H->>M: Collect metrics
    M-->>H: Return status
    alt Healthy
        H->>R: Proceed
    else Unhealthy
        H->>R: Rollback
    end